          "id": "05f523348bc1cb53c01e0d756a167fa25be03a02",
          "message": "fix(build): include <unistd.h> for getpid() on macOS/iOS/ARM64\n\ngetpid() is POSIX, not implicitly declared on Apple platforms (clang\nstrict headers). Fixes CT ARM64, iOS, and macOS CI build failures.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
