          "distinct": true,
          "id": "f814b60d03614d44cfab665717aac69b2cbf3a22",
          "message": "fix: clear Semgrep and -Werror CI failures\n\n- adaptor.cpp: nosemgrep on public_key.scalar_mul — false positive,\n  public_key is not a secret; CT concern applies to secrets only\n- musig2.cpp: nosemgrep on agg_nonce.R2.scalar_mul — false positive,\n  aggregated nonce commitment is a public value, not a secret\n- test_musig2.cpp: remove unused pk1/pk2 (xonly pubkeys never consumed)\n  to fix -Werror=unused-but-set-variable in Security Audit build\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-27T08:10:35Z",
