          "id": "2d5a962bf210ad4a42703c9146ebd8d7557b50a4",
          "message": "fix(audit): P2 test coverage — demote secp256k1_* shim ABI functions to WARN\n\nsecp256k1_* shim functions are tested via standalone shim tests that\ndon't route through the unified runner call graph. The check now\nreports them as WARN (not FAIL) with an explanation that they are\ncovered by check_libsecp_shim_parity.py and dedicated standalone\nshim tests. ufsecp_* functions without coverage remain FAIL.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
